Package: rwevalidate
Title: Validate Patient Cohorts for Real-World Evidence Studies on OMOP CDM
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Hamid", "Tavakoli", email = "htavakoli@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Validates instantiated patient cohorts on an OMOP Common Data
    Model database for real-world-evidence (RWE) studies. From a single
    function call it produces a structured HTML and JSON validation report
    aligned with FDA RWE guidance (Relevance and Reliability) and HARPER
    protocol requirements, covering concept coverage, cohort attrition,
    temporal data density, and covariate feasibility against a comparator.
